ASoC: rsnd: use union with rsnd_dmaen / rsnd_dmapp

Renesas R-Car needs 2 DMACs.1st DMAC is DMAEngine, and 2nd DMAC is
implemented as local code. These 2 DMACs are never shared.
We can use union for these.

